text: Annabel Breuer (born 23 October 1992) is a German wheelchair basketball player. She won a gold medal at the 2012 Summer Paralympics, and silver medal at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. She played at the 2011 Women's U25 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship, 2015 Women's U25 Wheelchair Basketball World Championship, and 2014 Women's World Wheelchair Basketball Championship. == References == Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic gold medalists for Germany Category:Paralympic silver medalists for Germany Category:German wheelchair basketball players
